| **RC522 Pin** | **NodeMCU Pin** | **Function**     |
| ------------- | --------------- | ---------------- |
| **3.3V**      | 3V3             | Power supply     |
| **GND**       | GND             | Ground           |
| **SDA**       | **D2 (GPIO4)**  | SS / Chip Select |
| **SCK**       | **D5 (GPIO14)** | SPI Clock        |
| **MOSI**      | **D7 (GPIO13)** | SPI MOSI         |
| **MISO**      | **D6 (GPIO12)** | SPI MISO         |
| **RST**       | **D1 (GPIO5)**  | Reset pin        |

